snippet.title: I Love You Freddy! (2023) (Official Trailer) - 4K
snippet.description:
We are happy to present to you our very first comedy game "I Love You Freddy!" A satire comedy about an obsessive fan girl who traps her idol Freddy on an island, as freddy must figure out a way to escape.

Find our game on steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2692800/I_Love_You_Freddy/

Follow us for more updates:

Instagram: @madwritergames 
Tiktok: @madwritergames
